<span id="freeTextContainer14587200306935976483">The scope of this book is amazing. You have a sense of foreboding reading this because you have the benefit(?)of knowing what will happen to this region over the next 75 years. The shadow of WWII hangs over this and adds even more intensity. I can&apos;t forget the words of an old woman in Montenegro; &quot;If I had to live, why should my life have been like this?&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText14587200306935976483" style="display:none">The scope of this book is amazing. You have a sense of foreboding reading this because you have the benefit(?)of knowing what will happen to this region over the next 75 years. The shadow of WWII hangs over this and adds even more intensity. I can't forget the words of an old woman in Montenegro; "If I had to live, why should my life have been like this?"</span>
